<span id="freeTextContainer4244584273434870016">A classic from the Psychedelic Era.<br/><br/>Huxley goes into detail about his fascinating experiences with the mind expanding substance, mescalin. <br/><br/>This is basically the whole premise of this essay, him describing the results of mescalin ingestion on himself.<br/><br/>A thought-provoking and interesting read.</span>

