<li class='cover' id='bookCover_123698'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/123698.The_Psychedelic_Experience"><img alt="The Psychedelic Experience: A Manual Based on the Tibetan Book of the Dead" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1348547775l/123698._SX98_.jpg" />
